# Fullstack standards (backend workspace)

When editing C# in this repository, follow the Agent Skill **senior-dotnet-angular-fullstack** at `.cursor/skills/senior-dotnet-angular-fullstack/SKILL.md` (Clean Architecture, module boundaries, CQRS/MediatR, FluentValidation, thin controllers, EF Core boundaries, Result pattern).

For Angular UI work, open the **GymBroPortal** repository and use its `.cursor/rules/angular-frontend.mdc` and **figma-design-system.mdc** together with the same skill.

